         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">December 30  ¶  ¶ [186]3 ¶ editorial addition. ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ The Council of the Acclimatisation Society having decided to hold a monthly evening meeting of the Members of the Society I am directed by the...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">63.12.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From George Sprigg</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 63/934, unit 3, p. 359, VPRS 2225 outward letterpress copy books, Acclimatisation Society of Victoria, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">December 30 <space unit="chars" quantity="2"/>[186]3<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">editorial addition</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The Council of the Acclimatisation Society having decided to hold a monthly evening meeting of the Members of the Society I am directed by the Council to enquire whether the Hall of the Royal Society could be lent to the Council for this purpose. The evening named is the first Tuesday in each month after the full moon. I would just state that the suggestion of asking for the Royal Society was first [invited] by two or three members of that Society. Waiting the favor of a reply<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">Reply not found, but a</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">t the meeting of the Council of the Acclimatisation Society held on 5 January 1864 'a letter was read from the Royal Society, granting the use of their hall</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">
                           <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">for the evening meetings of the Acclimatisation Society, provided all expenses was defrayed by the Society. The secretary was directed to write and thank the Royal Society for the concession, and to intimate that any members of that society would be gladly welcomed to the proposed meetings (</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont"
                             style="font-style: italic; color: #0070C0; ">Argus</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">, 7 January 1864, p.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">5)</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">.</seg>
                     </p>
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; color: #C00000; "
                        xml:lang="en">Is there an out-letter book in the archives of the RSV? If so this letter should be there.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have honor to be</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most Obedt Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Geo Sprigg</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Secretary</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">To Dr Mueller F.R.S.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Hony Secretary Royal Society</p>
         </div>
